{"tid":247302,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡古即將加盟車路士","createTime":"2017-05-17T16:22:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T08:10:35.000Z","uid":57035,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"488422f16917d32c81e79eb0a134438b7aef4a73","tid":247302,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i3.liverpoolecho.co.uk/incoming/article10491209.ece/ALTERNATES/s615/JS77145758.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.liverpoolecho.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle10491209.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs615%2FJS77145758.jpg&h=41bf26b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【nowSports新聞組】比利時國腳盧卡古即將加盟車路士，消息獲得安德列治的官方證實。<br />\n<br />\n車路士一直垂涎比利時球會安德列治的18歲前鋒盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku），現今終於達成轉會協議。安德列治在官網中表示：「安德列治和車路士已就盧卡古的轉會達成協議，他將會成為該倫敦球會的一份子。」<br />\n<br />\n安德列治的經理雲賀斯比克亦表示：「我們不想看到盧卡古離開，他是球會發掘兼培育的人才，但這交易對所有人來說都有好處。我們將會找到他的替代品。」<br />\n<br />\n車路士領隊保亞斯在周六友賽3：1贏格拉斯哥流浪的賽後，被問及盧卡古時亦指：「甚麼事也有可能。」<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：&copy; AFP）<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp149565217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp149565217&d=k77hOMsO7CBmOnyTOgf%2B4UbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=894811a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp149565217&h=987e9b0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp149565217</a>"},{"pid":"0c529c5fefd9c023fa25efb49eca078123ec8b1d","tid":247302,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5aefc280eff3bbc689e12175278f1ad8d8e6dc5","tid":247302,"uid":138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small